  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As an Attack action, you load and fire shells that burst into shrapnel upon impact. Choose a target location within range. Each creature in a 4m-radius sphere centered on the point of impact of the shell must make a Dexterity saving throw (DC 8 + proficiency bonus + DEX modifier). A target takes 2d6 piercing damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p>You have 3 charges of Flak Cannon. You regain all of your charges on a long rest.</p>\n<p>This feature's damage increases by 2d6 when you reach 5th level (4d6), 11th level (6d6), 17th level (8d6)</p>",
